<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="scare-vt">scare <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /skeə(r)/    美 /sker/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-frighten">1.★ <strong>使恐惧；使害怕 (frighten)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The thunder scared the children. 
雷声吓着了那些孩子。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="scare-away-off">scare … away / off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…吓跑</strong>  </p></div>